7
00:02:06,542 --> 00:02:11,343
"This delicate heat
of autumn we bear..."

8
00:02:11,447 --> 00:02:16,510
"...lying in the courtyard."

9
00:02:17,387 --> 00:02:27,524
"We pull off of the shade of
the veil from your eyes..."

10
00:02:27,730 --> 00:02:39,198
"We lay on our stomachs,
tossing and turning."

11
