named Kajli live here?

724
01:02:33,822 --> 01:02:37,758
I want to meet her.

725
01:02:38,060 --> 01:02:41,860
She is resting now; a customer
has just left. She is tired.

726
01:02:41,964 --> 01:02:47,368
Will someone else do?
- I have some work with her.

727
01:02:50,806 --> 01:02:55,869
Everyone has the
same work. Come.

728
01:03:01,083 --> 01:03:05,884
Get up. - Who is it? - 
Go inside and sleep. Sit.

729
01:03:17,833 --> 01:03:22,896
Kajli, get up. Someone
has come for you. Get up.

730
01:03:24,840 --> 01:03:29,743
Let me sleep, auntie. How
much will you make me toil?

731
01:03:30,112 --> 01:03:32,808
Get up, child. He seems
to be a very rich man.

732
01:03:32,915 --> 01:03:35,076
If he was a pauper, I myself
would have shooed him off.

733
01:03:37,853 --> 01:03:40,822
I do not think he will sit.
He'll have fun you and go away.

734
01:03:40,923 --> 01:03:44,916
Meet him. And do not agree to
anything less than 30 or 40.

735
01:04:17,893 --> 01:04:21,954
Hey sir, you were
so late in coming.

736
01:04:22,898 --> 01:04:29,804
I am yawning. Sit.

737
01:05:02,204 --> 01:05:03,831
Will you have
something to drink?

738
01:05:05,941 --> 01:05:11,345
No whisky. But I have country
beer, like myself. Will it do?

739
01:05:12,948 --> 01:05:17,851
No, daughter. I
just came to meet you.

740
01:05:17,953 --> 01:05:20,854
Why do you call me daughter?
Just come down to business.

741
01:05:22,958 --> 01:05:27,019
I have come here with
some other work, daughter.

742
01:05:27,129 --> 01:05:31,031
Don't tell daughter. I
have heard lot of this.

743
01:05:31,967 --> 01:05:34,026
Tell me if you want to sit.

744
01:05:34,136 --> 01:05:35,467
What is your name?

745
01:05:35,571 --> 01:05:37,539
What will you do with
my name? Do you want...

746
01:05:37,639 --> 01:05:39,197
...to take me home? Why
know about my ancestors?

747
01:05:39,308 --> 01:05:41,208
My mother was mad,
my father was lame.

748
01:05:41,977 --> 01:05:43,945
Want to ask something more?

749
01:05:44,046 --> 01:05:45,877
Why are you
getting angry, daughter?

750
01:05:47,983 --> 01:05:53,046
Auntie... auntie...

751
01:05:54,990 --> 01:05:56,890
Listen to me.

752
01:05:56,992 --> 01:05:58,960
You only take care
of this old man.

753
01:05:59,061 --> 01:06:00,961
He has come to adopt me.

754
01:06:21,016 --> 01:06:22,074
What happened?

755
01:06:23,118 --> 01:06:24,415
Come on inside.

756
01:06:49,311 --> 01:06:51,472
Is Kajli there?

757
01:06:52,047 --> 01:07:03,288
Kajli... See your old
man has come. Go. Go.

758
01:07:17,072 --> 01:07:18,471
So you came back?

759
01:07:20,075 --> 01:07:21,975
Listen to what I
have to say, daughter.

760
01:07:22,077 --> 01:07:26,309
Daughter again?
Go. Get out. Go away.

761
01:07:26,415 --> 01:07:32,149
Where do these people come from?

762
01:07:32,254 --> 01:07:33,312
These people...

763
01:08:11,560 --> 01:08:16,020
What is it? What
do you want now?

764
01:08:18,133 --> 01:08:24,368
I want Kajli. I have whisky.
I need soda. Can I get it?

765
01:08:32,247 --> 01:08:36,445
So you have come on
the right path. Come.

766
01:08:47,829 --> 01:08:50,389
Sit. I'll bring the soda.

767
01:09:00,175 --> 01:09:03,144
What is it? What is your name?
- Paro.

768
01:09:03,245 --> 01:09:06,408
Will you take some whisky, sir?
- No.

769
01:09:08,183 --> 01:09:13,246
So you too are bonkers for
Kajli! She is quite an item.

770
01:09:13,355 --> 01:09:17,086
Once you are addicted to her,
you can have no one else.

771
01:09:17,459 --> 01:09:20,087
Husain, did you like anyone?

772
01:09:20,195 --> 01:09:22,425
None from this lot.
- Then go inside. Go.

773
01:09:22,531 --> 01:09:24,089
Come on, let's play poker.

774
01:09:24,199 --> 01:09:26,258
Do you have money?
- Certainly.

775
01:09:26,368 --> 01:09:29,098
Can I come also? - Be seated
there. It is strictly cash here.

776
01:09:29,471 --> 01:09:31,098
Here, this is mine.

777
01:09:32,207 --> 01:09:35,267
Distribute for me. I'll
come just now. - Come soon.

778
01:09:40,215 --> 01:09:42,115
Is there any place
to sit separately?

779
01:09:42,217 --> 01:09:45,277
Yes. It will take Rs. 5 more.

780
01:09:45,387 --> 01:09:49,289
Doesn't matter.
- Come on. Bring the soda.

781
01:09:49,825 --> 01:09:51,452
Go, sir. Go.

782
01:10:00,502 --> 01:10:02,163
Sit down.

783
01:10:25,527 --> 01:10:27,154
Since when do you drink?

784
01:10:27,529 --> 01:10:31,158
Since I am in this job. The
one who would come earlier...

785
01:10:31,266 --> 01:10:35,327
...used to give me forcibly.
Now it has become a habit.

786
01:10:35,604 --> 01:10:38,164
If I don't drink,
I cannot sleep.

787
01:10:42,277 --> 01:10:44,177
You didn't touch the glasses.

788
01:10:48,617 --> 01:10:50,175
Cheers!

789
01:10:51,286 --> 01:10:53,186
What did you say?

790
01:10:53,722 --> 01:10:55,349
Nothing.

791
01:11:02,564 --> 01:11:04,191
Kajli!

792
01:11:05,567 --> 01:11:07,535
What is it, auntie?
- Listen.

793
01:11:10,305 --> 01:11:12,603
Will he sit the
whole night or go?

794
01:11:12,707 --> 01:11:15,369
I don't know.
- Ask him.

795
01:11:15,477 --> 01:11:20,210
Why? - Chawdhary has come.
He doesn't go to anyone...

796
01:11:20,315 --> 01:11:21,543
...but you.

797
01:11:21,650 --> 01:11:24,710
What do I do, auntie?
He's sitting. Tell him...

798
01:11:24,819 --> 01:11:26,286
...someone took me outside.

799
01:11:29,324 --> 01:11:31,724
Come on, why are you fretting.

800
01:11:32,327 --> 01:11:35,558
Chawdhary, she is
sitting with a client.

801
01:11:35,664 --> 01:11:37,291
Let me show.

802
01:11:42,604 --> 01:11:47,234
Chawdhary! What are you doing?

803
01:11:47,342 --> 01:11:49,572
It's a very rich
client you have trapped.

804
01:11:49,778 --> 01:11:52,246
You sit with him Kajli.
I shall deal with him.

805
01:11:52,347 --> 01:11:53,746
Come on with me.
- What will you take?

806
01:11:59,688 --> 01:12:01,417
Many people come here.

807
01:12:02,624 --> 01:12:05,422
Some days many people come
here. But on some other days...

808
01:12:05,527 --> 01:12:07,427
...it is so empty here, do
not even ask about them.

809
01:12:07,629 --> 01:12:09,756
People do not come
here even to just drink.

810
01:12:12,367 --> 01:12:16,667
But that Gangu Rani, she
takes good care of the girls.

811
01:12:16,805 --> 01:12:20,673
Just like a mother
she treats them. Drink.

812
01:12:20,775 --> 01:12:22,606
You are very slow.

813
01:12:23,378 --> 01:12:25,346
What's the hurry?

814
01:12:25,814 --> 01:12:27,782
Will you stay the whole night?

815
01:12:31,987 --> 01:12:38,449
Yes. Do you go out also?

816
01:12:38,660 --> 01:12:42,460
Yes. If he is atrustworthy
man, Gangu Rani sends me.

817
01:12:42,564 --> 01:12:44,623
What does trustworthy mean?

818
01:12:44,833 --> 01:12:48,291
Gangu Rani looks at
the man and understands.

819
01:12:48,403 --> 01:12:50,371
She has seen in a lot in life.

820
01:12:54,676 --> 01:12:56,473
Will she send you with me?

821
01:12:58,513 --> 01:13:00,310
It appears so.

822
01:13:02,417 --> 01:13:05,818
Not for just one night.
For many days.

823
01:13:08,423 --> 01:13:09,822
Out of the city?

824
01:13:09,924 --> 01:13:12,722
No, in this city only.

825
01:13:13,862 --> 01:13:17,491
As long as I am in this city.

826
01:13:24,706 --> 01:13:31,839
I understand. I have also seen
life. But it will cost a lot.

827
01:13:31,946 --> 01:13:36,508
Do not worry about money. I
will give as much as you ask.

828
01:13:37,452 --> 01:13:41,354
But you will have to stay
with me where I tell you.

829
01:13:41,456 --> 01:13:43,686
Agreed. Okay.

830
01:13:49,564 --> 01:13:51,532
Tell me, from when.

831
01:13:52,467 --> 01:13:53,695
From today.

832
01:13:57,472 --> 01:13:59,702
How much will you take? Tell me.

833
01:14:02,744 --> 01:14:09,547
Shall I call Gangu Rani?
You'll give an advance. No drugs.

834
01:14:09,651 --> 01:14:11,380
Call her.

835
01:14:36,511 --> 01:14:37,910
You sleep.

836
01:14:40,515 --> 01:14:42,005
Dinner, sir?

837
01:14:42,117 --> 01:14:45,575
I have eaten. You sleep.
Turn off the lights.

838
01:14:59,534 --> 01:15:02,765
Where are we?

839
01:16:04,916 --> 01:16:07,885
Good morning, sir.
- Good morning.

840
01:16:10,922 --> 01:16:13,550
Keep the tea
outside in the lawn.

841
01:16:44,956 --> 01:16:48,084
Good morning, sir.
- Good morning.

842
01:16:48,793 --> 01:16:51,591
I waited for you
till late at night.

843
01:16:51,696 --> 01:16:55,188
Yes, I was delayed.

844
01:17:01,706 --> 01:17:03,765
Those papers which have
come from the office...

845
01:17:03,875 --> 01:17:07,777
...I have signed them and kept.
You can take them and return.

846
01:17:08,146 --> 01:17:12,105
Take Dhyan Singh also with
you. I shall not need him.

847
01:17:12,984 --> 01:17:17,114
Tell in the office not todisturb
me at all these vacations.

848
01:17:17,722 --> 01:17:20,156
I do not know
when I shall return.

849
01:17:20,725 --> 01:17:24,786
Tell Kiran to mind the business.

850
01:17:27,999 --> 01:17:30,627
Do you want to ask anything?
- No.

851
01:17:35,740 --> 01:17:40,643
You woke up? - Yes. I
got much drunk last night.

852
01:17:42,013 --> 01:17:44,140
You go. Make
preparations for your return.

853
01:17:47,752 --> 01:17:50,152
This whisky is a
very miserable thing.

854
01:17:50,255 --> 01:17:52,155
Look, do not swear.

855
01:17:53,758 --> 01:17:56,727
I have sworn at whisky, not you.

856
01:17:57,028 --> 01:18:01,055
It may be for the whisky; but
girls don't look good cussing.

857
01:18:01,766 --> 01:18:05,668
Whether it is a boy or a girl,
a swear word is a swear word.

858
01:18:05,870 --> 01:18:07,735
What is good in that?

859
01:18:13,044 --> 01:18:16,013
Let us get some new
clothes for you today.

860
01:18:16,314 --> 01:18:19,010
I have some.
They are in the box.

861
01:18:19,217 --> 01:18:23,017
Even then, let me buy
some more. - Buy them.

862
01:18:23,121 --> 01:18:26,181
What loss it is to me? But
do not cut it from my fees.

863
01:18:28,893 --> 01:18:31,020
You are good at business.

864
01:18:34,399 --> 01:18:37,698
What else? If you have to
sell your body to live...

865
01:18:37,802 --> 01:18:39,895
...then you'll know.

866
01:18:41,072 --> 01:18:45,099
What are you doing?
- What?

867
01:18:45,210 --> 01:18:47,041
Why are you smoking a beedi?

868
01:18:47,812 --> 01:18:51,213
I smoke beedi.

869
01:18:53,818 --> 01:18:57,049
That may be. But is
it a problem if you...

870
01:18:57,155 --> 01:18:59,783
...do not smoke here
in front of everybody?

871
01:19:00,425 --> 01:19:04,725
Look friend, this will be
very difficult. You've paid me...

872
01:19:04,829 --> 01:19:08,458
...but do not boss on
me as if I am your wife.

873
01:19:08,566 --> 01:19:11,797
Do not smoke; do not swear;
don't do this; don't do that.

874
01:19:13,171 --> 01:19:17,073
For what you have paid me,
that I know and you know too.

875
01:19:19,444 --> 01:19:25,076
Look, if you feel so much
like smoking, then go inside.

876
01:19:26,117 --> 01:19:29,143
Outside there are servants.
People look.

877
01:19:29,387 --> 01:19:33,915
If you keep my respect among
them, it will be a favour.

878
01:19:34,959 --> 01:19:39,760
Otherwise, let's bathe and go
out. Where do I refuse there?

879
01:19:42,867 --> 01:19:45,768
I get humiliated very
much with a respectable man.

880
01:19:52,877 --> 01:19:55,175
Sir, you have a
trunk call from Calcutta.

881
01:20:01,152 --> 01:20:05,851
Hello. Speak Kiran.
I am all right.

882
01:20:06,891 --> 01:20:14,127
I have money. I'll ask
if I need. And listen...

883
01:20:14,232 --> 01:20:20,137
I am sending Mathur and Kiran
back. Oh, don't you bother...

884
01:20:20,238 --> 01:20:27,144
...and don't bother me also.
What? Okay, you sign it. Okay.

885
01:20:29,914 --> 01:20:32,883
Sorry sir. I had to
disturb you in the morning.

886
01:20:32,984 --> 01:20:35,885
I'm going back today. I
thought of meeting you.

887
01:20:35,987 --> 01:20:38,353
If you need anything from
Calcutta, you can tell me.

888
01:20:39,924 --> 01:20:41,152
Sir...

889
01:20:41,926 --> 01:20:43,985
Sir...
- What is it?

890
01:20:44,095 --> 01:20:46,222
Where is the box of my clothes?

891
01:20:47,932 --> 01:20:50,332
In my drunkenness, I
lost my wits only.

892
01:20:52,203 --> 01:20:56,833
It is outside in the car. Tell
the driver. He'll remove it.

893
01:20:58,943 --> 01:21:01,173
So, when are you going?

894
01:21:01,279 --> 01:21:04,840
I thought of meeting you. - Will
you have tea? - No, I'll go now.

895
01:21:04,949 --> 01:21:09,045
I wouldn't want to disturb you
much. Have a good time, sir.

896
01:21:18,062 --> 01:21:20,189
I got it. It was in the car.

897
01:21:20,298 --> 01:21:22,528
Did you have to ask now only?
- What happened?

898
01:21:23,968 --> 01:21:28,871
Don't you have anything
else to wear? Like some saris?

899
01:21:29,974 --> 01:21:32,204
You go, get ready.
We'll go to the bazaar.

900
01:21:50,094 --> 01:21:53,222
Look, how beautiful
you look like this.

901
01:21:53,331 --> 01:21:55,891
Unnecessarily you
put all the makeup.

902
01:21:56,000 --> 01:22:00,903
You speak like a lover. No
one has told me this before.

903
01:22:01,272 --> 01:22:04,241
Can't you speak
without calling names?

904
01:22:05,009 --> 01:22:07,307
If you feel bad, I
shan't say so, my friend.

905
01:22:11,015 --> 01:22:14,576
Wear one of these saris.
Which one will you wear?

906
01:22:15,019 --> 01:22:17,249
The one that you like.

907
01:22:19,023 --> 01:22:21,253
You wear it. I'll go outside.

908
01:22:21,359 --> 01:22:25,261
Why do you go out? I shall
wear it in front of you, friend.

909
01:22:25,363 --> 01:22:27,263
Won't you feel ashamed
to change in front of me?

910
01:22:27,365 --> 01:22:30,129
Your daughter may get
ashamed. Why should I?

911
01:22:31,035 --> 01:22:33,936
People spend so much
money for the body.

912
01:22:34,038 --> 01:22:39,943
Will it always remain like this?
I was going to call you a name.

913
01:22:40,044 --> 01:22:42,945
You wear. I'll go outside.

914
01:22:43,047 --> 01:22:50,283
I understood you. - What? -
You are another type of man.

915
01:22:50,488 --> 01:22:52,012
Another type?

916
01:22:53,324 --> 01:22:56,293
Yes, the romantic. They
keep girls only for roaming...

917
01:22:56,394 --> 01:23:00,023
...drinking and dancing.
Isn't that true?

918
01:23:00,331 --> 01:23:02,959
Yes. I am that
other type of man.

919
01:23:04,068 --> 01:23:06,969
But you have
committed a mistake. - What?

920
01:23:07,071 --> 01:23:09,301
It would have been better
if you'd have chosen Champa.

921
01:23:09,407 --> 01:23:15,312
She dances quite well. She
taught me, but I didn't learn.

922
01:23:15,413 --> 01:23:21,147
But I'll show you.
- Okay. Wear the sari.

