"My lover, get aside,
get aside, get aside..."

946
01:26:10,855 --> 01:26:19,320
"I sway a lot in my love... My
lover, get aside... get aside..."

947
01:26:19,430 --> 01:26:21,660
"If I wink..."

948
01:26:22,266 --> 01:26:23,665
Enough, Kajli.

949
01:26:24,268 --> 01:26:27,829
I am doing this for you. You
are spending so much on me.

950
01:26:27,939 --> 01:26:31,568
Do not worry about my money.
I have a lot of it.

951
01:26:32,276 --> 01:26:34,506
Ask how much you want.

952
01:26:34,812 --> 01:26:36,370
What do I want to do?

953
01:26:36,547 --> 01:26:39,675
If I get for my food and
booze, enough. What else?

954
01:26:42,286 --> 01:26:44,186
Will you drink some?

955
01:26:44,555 --> 01:26:46,853
No. Not today.

956
01:26:46,958 --> 01:26:48,357
Are you sick?

957
01:26:48,559 --> 01:26:52,359
No. Is it necessary
man should drink daily.

958
01:26:52,730 --> 01:26:54,357
I'll not be able
to drink, friend.

959
01:26:55,299 --> 01:26:57,199
Try abstaining for one day.

960
