You will make me
go out of business.

961
01:26:59,637 --> 01:27:01,798
When I was not doing all this,
someone used to come...

962
01:27:01,906 --> 01:27:05,205
...and make me do all
this forcibly. But now...

963
01:27:05,309 --> 01:27:09,712
...somehow you have come.
Why did you not come then?

964
01:27:10,915 --> 01:27:12,212
When?

965
01:27:12,650 --> 01:27:14,277
When I was young.

966
01:27:14,752 --> 01:27:19,621
I could not come then. I
am repenting for that now.

967
01:27:20,324 --> 01:27:23,225
But if you'd have come then,
we would not have gelled.

968
01:27:23,761 --> 01:27:26,229
Why? - But you would
have gelled with my mother...

969
01:27:26,330 --> 01:27:28,560
...because she was
also very beautiful.

970
01:27:31,335 --> 01:27:33,235
What was your mother doing?

971
01:27:34,605 --> 01:27:38,564
She was just dying. She
kept dying for twenty years.

972
01:27:38,676 --> 01:27:40,576
For some scoundrel of a doctor.

973
01:27:42,346 --> 01:27:47,249
But don't remind me of all that.
Do not ever talk of my family.

974
01:27:47,351 --> 01:27:49,410
I'll warn you
against that now only.

975
01:27:53,357 --> 01:27:55,757
I do not feel naked
sitting among naked people now...

976
01:27:55,860 --> 01:28:00,422
...but I do feel ashamed
among respectable folk.

977
01:28:01,365 --> 01:28:03,424
I can then see my nakedness.

978
01:28:03,534 --> 01:28:06,332
You only had gone
and sat in nakedness.

979
01:28:06,437 --> 01:28:09,668
Come back to where
you had gone from.

980
01:28:12,376 --> 01:28:14,435
Do you not know of the cobbler...

981
01:28:14,545 --> 01:28:17,275
...who spent a
lifetime working in leather?

982
01:28:17,381 --> 01:28:20,612
The day he passed by a
perfumery, he fainted.

983
01:28:24,388 --> 01:28:27,289
He had gone there after
many days; that's why.

984
01:28:27,825 --> 01:28:29,690
If he goes there daily,
then he will not faint.

985
01:28:29,794 --> 01:28:32,285
It isn't needed at
all. If one feels...

986
01:28:32,396 --> 01:28:34,830
...naked going somewhere,
why should they go there?

987
01:28:37,401 --> 01:28:41,303
I will have to travel to the
market of perfumes so many...

988
01:28:41,405 --> 01:28:43,635
...times, you will forget
the stench of leather.

989
01:28:45,409 --> 01:28:47,639
You must have gone to
some other paths too.

990
01:28:49,413 --> 01:28:53,372
Not all the time... - Sir...
this was left in the both room.

991
01:28:58,422 --> 01:29:00,322
This... is this yours?

992
01:29:01,525 --> 01:29:02,822
Yes.

993
01:29:07,431 --> 01:29:09,399
Why do you wear this coral.

994
01:29:11,435 --> 01:29:13,665
Someone had given it to me.

995
01:29:14,872 --> 01:29:16,339
Who had?

996
01:29:16,440 --> 01:29:18,670
Some one.
- Is he not there any longer?

997
01:29:18,776 --> 01:29:23,679
He is there. I don't
know how and where he is.

998
01:29:25,449 --> 01:29:27,349
What is his name?

999
01:29:28,452 --> 01:29:29,851
Kundan.

1000
01:29:30,454 --> 01:29:34,515
Do you want to
search for him? Do you?

1001
01:29:34,625 --> 01:29:37,423
Why are you
worried about my life?

1002
01:29:37,528 --> 01:29:40,429
Do you want some alcohol?
Shall I bring the glass?

1003
01:29:57,815 --> 01:30:00,545
I look dignified
with you now, isn't it?

1004
01:30:02,586 --> 01:30:05,384
There is something.
You are a good man.

1005
01:30:05,489 --> 01:30:09,391
But you are useless for me.
- What do you mean?

1006
01:30:10,494 --> 01:30:12,894
Have you kept a
woman for the first time?

1007
01:30:14,498 --> 01:30:15,726
Yes.

1008
01:30:17,501 --> 01:30:19,469
Never married?

1009
01:30:20,604 --> 01:30:21,730
No.

1010
01:30:22,840 --> 01:30:24,398
Why?

1011
01:30:26,777 --> 01:30:31,737
It was a long time ago.
I loved a woman.

1012
01:30:33,117 --> 01:30:35,915
I wanted to come
back and marry her.

1013
01:30:37,021 --> 01:30:38,921
But... in those days...

1014
01:30:39,523 --> 01:30:44,426
A man was killed at my
hands during an operation.

1015
01:30:46,530 --> 01:30:48,430
Are you a doctor?

1016
01:30:48,532 --> 01:30:50,932
No. A surgeon.

1017
01:30:54,538 --> 01:30:58,497
There was a police case, and
I was jailed for three years.

1018
01:30:59,543 --> 01:31:03,946
Because of that shame, I
didn't tell her anything.

1019
01:31:04,815 --> 01:31:08,615
I didn't come back,
and neither did I marry.

1020
01:31:13,224 --> 01:31:16,625
Don't scratch your ears.
They get poisoned.

1021
01:31:19,563 --> 01:31:21,963
Don't scratch your ears.
They get poisoned.

1022
01:31:22,066 --> 01:31:25,467
Who told you that if you itch
your ears, they get poisoned?

1023
01:31:25,569 --> 01:31:29,630
Mother. Mother told it
to me. In my childhood.

1024
01:31:48,859 --> 01:31:50,656
Where are we going?

1025
01:31:51,595 --> 01:31:53,563
The blue valley.

1026
01:31:57,034 --> 01:31:58,831
Have you ever gone there?

1027
01:31:58,936 --> 01:32:01,905
Yes, in my childhood.

1028
01:32:03,607 --> 01:32:05,507
How is the place?

1029
01:32:05,609 --> 01:32:07,668
I just remember two places.

1030
01:32:07,945 --> 01:32:11,574
One is the company,
mother used to work there.

1031
01:32:11,882 --> 01:32:16,842
And the hospital, where
mother used to take me to.

1032
01:32:17,621 --> 01:32:18,849
Why?

1033
01:32:19,723 --> 01:32:24,683
She used to tell the
doctors to make me a doctor.

1034
01:32:26,630 --> 01:32:27,688
Then?

1035
01:32:27,798 --> 01:32:31,734
Then what. Does anyone want
a doctor without studying?

1036
01:32:33,637 --> 01:32:35,730
If you wish, you can
continue your studies.

1037
01:32:35,840 --> 01:32:37,205
You can become doctor.

1038
01:32:38,742 --> 01:32:41,870
Should I tell you something?
I hate the word doctor.

1039
01:32:42,179 --> 01:32:44,545
I don't hate that man
as much who made me...

1040
01:32:44,648 --> 01:32:47,879
...a prostitute, as much
as I hate that doctor...

1041
01:32:47,985 --> 01:32:49,885
...because of whom my
mother went crazy.

1042
01:32:52,756 --> 01:32:55,156
If I would meet him
once in this life...

1043
01:32:55,259 --> 01:32:57,887
Then? What would you do?

1044
01:32:58,095 --> 01:33:00,086
Even I don't know what I'd do.

1045
01:33:00,331 --> 01:33:04,734
I just know that whatever
I'd do would be very bad.

1046
01:33:10,107 --> 01:33:16,740
Rascal! Wretch!
- Oh god...

1047
01:33:16,847 --> 01:33:19,907
Get lost from here. Get lost.
- No, I won't... I won't...

1048
01:33:26,123 --> 01:33:28,250
What is going on? Why
are you two fighting?

1049
01:33:28,359 --> 01:33:33,126
Dare he hit me! I will
wreck his entire family.

1050
01:33:33,230 --> 01:33:34,993
I will...
- Silent, Kajli.

1051
01:33:35,699 --> 01:33:36,927
What is the matter?

1052
01:33:37,034 --> 01:33:39,764
Sir, I told her not to
come in the kitchen.

1053
01:33:39,870 --> 01:33:41,269
But she didn't listen to me.

1054
01:33:41,372 --> 01:33:43,602
Who are you to refuse me?
Is this your father's house?

1055
01:33:43,707 --> 01:33:45,607
See, sir... when I told her
to go out of the kitchen...

1056
01:33:45,709 --> 01:33:47,609
...she abused me on my mother.

1057
01:33:47,711 --> 01:33:49,144
Why did you send her separate?

1058
01:33:50,714 --> 01:33:54,616
See, sir... I have been
silent till today because of you.

1059
01:33:55,052 --> 01:33:57,612
Otherwise, you
know it very well.

1060
01:33:57,721 --> 01:34:00,121
I cannot eat
anything that she touches.

1061
01:34:00,324 --> 01:34:02,952
If you can eat it,
please have her cook it.

1062
01:34:03,727 --> 01:34:07,128
I will have her cook it.
Go away from here.

1063
01:34:07,331 --> 01:34:10,960
This is not correct, sir. A
respectable man like you...

1064
01:34:11,068 --> 01:34:13,036
You don't have to
worry about my respect.

1065
01:34:13,137 --> 01:34:14,968
I will take care
of my own respect.

1066
01:34:15,739 --> 01:34:17,639
Please leave.

1067
01:34:24,748 --> 01:34:26,147
Come with me.

1068
01:34:38,762 --> 01:34:40,662
I threw the cook away.

1069
01:34:40,764 --> 01:34:42,664
To hell with the wretch.

1070
01:34:42,766 --> 01:34:44,825
And which wretch
will cook the good?

1071
01:34:44,935 --> 01:34:47,665
I will cook the food,
don't I know how to?

1072
01:34:50,774 --> 01:34:53,675
Eat it and see. You
will forget this wretch.

1073
01:34:53,877 --> 01:34:58,007
Is it? Okay. Bring it. Come on.

1074
01:36:10,854 --> 01:36:12,754
Are you going to Dholpur?

1075
01:36:12,856 --> 01:36:16,155
Yes. I think that is
the name of that place.

1076
01:36:17,127 --> 01:36:18,822
What work do you have there?

1077
01:36:20,864 --> 01:36:22,263
I want to search
for a man there.

1078
01:36:22,866 --> 01:36:24,766
What is the name of that person?

1079
01:36:25,869 --> 01:36:29,965
Kundan.
- Why? - I have some work.

1080
01:36:30,074 --> 01:36:31,302
What is the work?

1081
01:36:31,475 --> 01:36:34,933
Not me, but you can
have some work with him.

1082
01:36:35,045 --> 01:36:38,446
No, I don't have any work,
I don't want to meet him.

1083
01:36:44,988 --> 01:36:48,947
You loved Kundan, isn't it?

1084
01:36:49,226 --> 01:36:50,853
Yes, so?

1085
01:36:51,228 --> 01:36:54,197
What if Kundan is
still waiting for you?

1086
01:36:54,898 --> 01:36:57,128
Nobody waits for
anybody for so long.

1087
01:36:58,902 --> 01:37:01,302
Didn't your mother
wait for a doctor?

1088
01:37:02,906 --> 01:37:04,305
Twenty years.

1089
01:37:07,177 --> 01:37:11,136
It isn't wrong to meet him once.

1090
01:37:12,015 --> 01:37:15,883
I am not worthy of
him anymore now.

1091
01:37:17,254 --> 01:37:19,814
And I will not hide
anything from him too.

1092
01:37:19,923 --> 01:37:23,984
It is possible that the
doctor thought like this...

1093
01:37:24,094 --> 01:37:26,824
...and he didn't return too.

1094
01:37:30,033 --> 01:37:36,165
If that doctor returned...
wouldn't your mother forgive him?

1095
01:38:01,231 --> 01:38:02,255
Yes?

1096
01:38:05,569 --> 01:38:08,197
Kundan... Kundan
stayed here, isn't it?

1097
01:38:08,305 --> 01:38:10,034
Yes, he stays here...

1098
01:38:11,975 --> 01:38:13,374
I... I...

1099
01:38:14,978 --> 01:38:16,878
I wanted to meet him.

1100
01:38:16,980 --> 01:38:18,880
He has gone out for some work.

1101
01:38:18,982 --> 01:38:21,041
Tell me. I am his wife.

1102
01:38:28,325 --> 01:38:30,054
So... he has married...

1103
01:38:35,265 --> 01:38:37,290
Can I tell you something, Kajli?

1104
01:38:39,002 --> 01:38:41,300
Why don't you marry someone too?

1105
01:38:42,339 --> 01:38:46,070
Someone nice...
- Who lets anyone remain nice?

1106
01:38:47,010 --> 01:38:51,413
No woman is a born prostitute.
You get people to make them.

1107
01:38:52,616 --> 01:38:55,915
I have got also.
- Who?

1108
01:38:56,286 --> 01:38:59,585
Dinu, my father's brother.

1109
01:39:00,290 --> 01:39:02,918
He used to regard me
as his daughter and...

1110
01:39:05,028 --> 01:39:07,258
Where was your
mother at that time?

1111
01:39:08,031 --> 01:39:13,333
Mother was crazy by
that time. Already crazy.

1112
01:39:16,039 --> 01:39:23,275
"The baton... how did
it stick to the neck?"

1113
01:39:23,480 --> 01:39:26,108
You have become crazy, Chanda.

1114
01:39:26,216 --> 01:39:28,116
Mother, go inside.

1115
01:39:41,064 --> 01:39:43,464
Dinu... Why did you
come once again?

1116
01:39:43,567 --> 01:39:48,129
I am your father's brother.
Regard me as your uncle.

1117
01:39:48,338 --> 01:39:50,306
How can you speak
to me like this?

1118
01:39:50,507 --> 01:39:53,305
I have seen your brotherhood.
I have told you so many times.

1119
01:39:53,410 --> 01:39:54,968
You don't need to
come here anymore.

1120
01:39:55,078 --> 01:39:58,309
Even if I do come, I
come to see your well being.

1121
01:39:58,415 --> 01:40:02,044
See, I have spoken to
the doctor upstairs.

1122
01:40:02,152 --> 01:40:04,382
Take Chanda and
have her admitted.

1123
01:40:05,088 --> 01:40:07,386
I don't want to send
mother to a mental asylum.

1124
01:40:07,491 --> 01:40:09,322
I will have her cured.

1125
01:40:10,360 --> 01:40:13,386
Uncle Moti...
- Yes?

1126
01:40:17,200 --> 01:40:20,067
Uncle, I am going to
get medicine for mother.

1127
01:40:20,170 --> 01:40:24,004
Please take care of her.
- What is all this?

1128
01:40:25,208 --> 01:40:30,168
When Kajli becomes a bride,
I will have her wear this.

1129
01:40:30,280 --> 01:40:32,544
I can make her a bride tomorrow.

1130
01:40:32,649 --> 01:40:34,514
But she should agree, isn't it?

1131
01:40:35,118 --> 01:40:40,021
How will you have her
married now? Are you crazy?

1132
01:40:40,557 --> 01:40:45,187
Let her become a doctor.
When she becomes a doctor...

1133
01:40:45,395 --> 01:40:48,364
I will give her this...
I will give her this...

1134
01:40:50,233 --> 01:40:53,532
You have ruined your
life for some doctor.

1135
01:40:54,137 --> 01:40:56,367
He must have died
a long time ago.

1136
01:40:56,473 --> 01:41:02,378
Kajli... hey, did Kajli
go to get the medicines?

1137
01:41:02,479 --> 01:41:05,380
She has gone to the school,
to become a doctor.

1138
01:41:05,482 --> 01:41:07,040
What is the work?

1139
01:41:07,417 --> 01:41:11,376
The landlord has called her.
Send her when she returns.

1140
01:41:12,756 --> 01:41:19,252
That landlord! Till when
will he save her? I'll see!

1141
01:41:19,596 --> 01:41:22,394
If I cannot do it right away...

1142
01:41:47,524 --> 01:41:50,425
You? What are you doing here?

1143
01:41:54,464 --> 01:41:56,261
What do you want?

1144
01:43:49,579 --> 01:43:53,538
While I was unconscious,
he took me to the city.

1145
01:43:54,751 --> 01:44:01,623
The dark room... and... and...

1146
01:44:11,334 --> 01:44:15,566
I was sold the day
I saw brightness.

1147
01:44:16,339 --> 01:44:18,398
At Gangurani's courtesan hall.

1148
01:44:25,682 --> 01:44:27,411
What did you do?

1149
01:44:28,952 --> 01:44:31,921
If I was with my
Kajli at that time...

1150
01:45:36,853 --> 01:45:38,320
Good morning.

1151
01:45:38,421 --> 01:45:44,656
Good morning. Yes... thank you.

1152
01:45:46,696 --> 01:45:48,664
You woke up
early in the morning?

1153
01:45:49,432 --> 01:45:51,866
My days and nights
have changed due to you.

1154
01:45:55,438 --> 01:45:59,670
I sleep early in the night,
and wake up quickly in the day.

1155
01:46:00,777 --> 01:46:05,680
I felt like praying
today in the morning.

1156
01:46:06,783 --> 01:46:11,846
You should have done it.
Do you know how to?

1157
01:46:14,457 --> 01:46:16,357
I didn't learn it at all.

1158
01:46:19,062 --> 01:46:22,691
Here...
- You have it. - Take this.

1159
01:46:22,799 --> 01:46:25,359
No. I had it lighted for you.

1160
01:46:27,470 --> 01:46:28,698
You will not have it?

1161
01:46:28,805 --> 01:46:32,366
No. You don't
like it. Therefore...

1162
01:46:32,475 --> 01:46:34,705
I thought that I'd not
have it in your presence.

1163
01:46:35,478 --> 01:46:37,878
That means, you will
have it if I am not around.

1164
01:46:40,483 --> 01:46:41,711
What?

1165
01:46:42,819 --> 01:46:46,550
Nothing, I forgot.

1166
01:46:47,490 --> 01:46:49,720
You will not be with me forever.

1167
01:46:50,760 --> 01:46:53,558
And if I tell you that I
will be with you forever.

1168
01:46:54,764 --> 01:46:58,564
I want to keep you
with me forever, then?

1169
01:47:00,670 --> 01:47:03,468
It is good for the number of
days that you are with me.

1170
01:47:04,507 --> 01:47:09,740
Don't promise me forever. I
am scared of such promises.

1171
01:47:11,514 --> 01:47:15,575
Someone had promised my
mother this once upon a time.

1172
01:47:15,785 --> 01:47:20,745
And I had promised
someone the second time.

1173
01:47:21,791 --> 01:47:23,088
Now...

1174
01:47:30,533 --> 01:47:33,434
There was so much
money here. Where is it?

1175
01:47:34,537 --> 01:47:39,440
The wallet too...
yes... I found them.

1176
01:47:40,643 --> 01:47:45,444
There was so much money... now,
there are just this much.

1177
01:47:46,649 --> 01:47:49,447
If you spend them like this,
you won't have any to return.

1178
01:47:50,086 --> 01:47:52,452
Shall I keep some
of them, carefully?

1179
01:47:56,159 --> 01:48:01,791
Kajli... many years ago, a
woman saved my money like this.

1180
01:48:02,899 --> 01:48:06,960
Even at that time, she kept
sixty rupees for my return.

1181
01:48:08,571 --> 01:48:13,474
If she wouldn't keep it, if
I wouldn't go... then... then...

1182
01:48:21,584 --> 01:48:24,485
I am feeling very strange.

1183
01:48:25,588 --> 01:48:29,490
When Kundan was here many
years ago, I felt like this.

1184
01:48:31,027 --> 01:48:34,155
Did you say something?
- No.

1185
01:49:14,070 --> 01:49:15,537
Where had you gone?

1186
01:49:17,640 --> 01:49:19,540
Are you still angry with me?

1187
01:49:20,643 --> 01:49:23,544
I committed a mistake,
forgive me.

1188
01:49:23,913 --> 01:49:25,540
I have come to take my clothes.

1189
01:49:25,648 --> 01:49:27,548
You will not get them.

1190
01:49:28,184 --> 01:49:33,884
You will not get your clothes,
salary or holiday. Nothing!

1191
01:49:35,658 --> 01:49:41,893
See, this house is yours, and
the owner of this house too.

1192
01:49:44,667 --> 01:49:46,567
I don't have anything here.

1193
01:49:47,937 --> 01:49:50,064
Nor the employer nor the house.

1194
01:49:50,673 --> 01:49:52,573
He has kept you to
look after the house.

1195
01:49:53,676 --> 01:49:55,576
You look after it.

1196
01:49:57,213 --> 01:50:03,584
You don't know why
and how we are kept?

1197
01:50:06,789 --> 01:50:08,916
Nobody gives us houses.

1198
01:50:09,125 --> 01:50:10,592
Then why have you come here?

1199
01:50:10,793 --> 01:50:12,920
To trouble a dignified man?

1200
01:50:16,799 --> 01:50:18,596
I had come here for my business.

1201
01:50:18,968 --> 01:50:22,927
And I forgot it.

